## Why this project?

It's small enough to finish in a day or two, but it establishes the complete workflow you'll use in larger applications:

* Qt/QML frontend
* C++ backend
* MAVSDK communication
* PX4 SITL
* Gazebo simulation

From there, every new feature (telemetry, commands, missions, camera feeds, etc.) builds on the same architecture.
